reviews.review_text:
5 star audience recording I love it when you have listened to a show for decades on a thin or multi-generational SBD recording and then you find one like this.  There are so many audience recordings that have come along lately to the Grateful Dead collection here at archive.org.   Start looking for the AUD copy upgrades.  You just gotta' poke around...
You will not be disappointed.  One of the best shows 1990 has to offer.  Spring Tour 1990 was bitter sweet knowing now that Brent would be gone just by mid-summer of that year.

if you are always looking for soundboard copies of Dead shows and are dismissive of audience recordings.....hit play and get back to me......

You want another prime example of an audience source that leaves any SBD in the dust, off my head?    3/2/1981.
